quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,"The Reality."
  69,2,"What is the Reality?"
  69,3,"And what can make yousg realize what the Reality is?"
  69,4,"Thamûd and ʻĀd disbelieved in  the Shocking Event."
  69,5,"So as for Thamûd, they were annihilated by the Overwhelming."
  69,6,"And as for ʻĀd, they were annihilated by a furious, roaring wind"
  69,7,"which He unleashed upon them for seven nights and eight days in succession, so yousg could see the people tossed around as though they were stumps of hollow palm trees."
  69,8,"So can yousg see any remnant of them?"